rule Bypass_Sample {
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass for sandbox/VM"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 56 8B 45 08 ?? ?? ?? ?? FF D2 }  // Likely bypassing a check on EBP/ESP
        $pattern1 = { 5E 5D C3 ?? ?? ?? ?? FF D2 }    // Bypassing a call check after EDX
        $pattern2 = { 8B 55 0C ?? ?? ?? ?? FF D0 }    // Bypassing a mov EAX check before FFD0 call

    condition:
        any_of(these)
}
